---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Enhanced Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-20 animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-brand rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-brand">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">À</span>
          </div>
          <div class="h-8 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-500 to-soul-500"></div>
          <div class="text-primary-600 font-semibold tracking-wider text-sm uppercase">Propos</div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
          <span data-i18n="about.title" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-primary-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Une voix, un parcours,</span>
          <br>
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500 to-soul-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent" data-i18n="about.titleAccent">une mission</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 mt-8">
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-accent-500 rounded-full"></div>
          <div class="text-accent-500 text-xl">♪</div>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500 to-soul-500 rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Enhanced Image Section -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="relative group">
            <!-- Background decorative elements -->
            <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-brand rounded-3xl transform rotate-3 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-500 opacity-20"></div>
            <div class="absolute -inset-2 bg-gradient-soul rounded-3xl transform -rotate-2 group-hover:-rotate-4 transition-transform duration-500 opacity-30"></div>
            
            <!-- Main image container -->
            <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl p-4 shadow-brand-lg group-hover:shadow-brand-lg transition-all duration-500">
              <img 
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1105666/pexels-photo-1105666.jpeg" 
                alt="Valentino Nguelieu en concert" 
                class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-80 md:h-96 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
              />
              
              <!-- Overlay with brand elements -->
              <div class="absolute top-8 left-8 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl px-4 py-2 shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-cameroon-green rounded-full"></div>
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-cameroon-red rounded-full"></div>
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-cameroon-yellow rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 ml-2">CAMEROUN</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="absolute bottom-8 right-8 bg-primary-600/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl px-4 py-2 shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-acadian-blue rounded-full"></div>
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-acadian-white rounded-full"></div>
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-acadian-red rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-white ml-2">ACADIE</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Enhanced Content Section -->
        <div class="space-y-8 animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="about.intro">
              Je m'appelle <strong class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 to-soul-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-bold">Valentino Nguelieu</strong>, artiste interprète originaire du Cameroun, actuellement basé au Nouveau-Brunswick, au Canada.
            </p>

            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="about.passion">
              Depuis tout petit, la musique a été pour moi plus qu'une passion — c'est un moyen d'expression, une thérapie, un langage universel.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-soul-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border-l-4 border-accent-500">
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="about.achievements">
                En 2024, j'ai eu l'honneur de remporter le concours <em class="text-accent-600 font-semibold">CCNB sur scène</em>, puis d'être sacré <em class="text-soul-600 font-semibold">Coup de cœur du public</em> au <strong>Gala de la chanson de Caraquet</strong>.
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="about.style">
              J'interprète principalement des chansons francophones aux influences blues, soul, et variétés. Mon univers est émotionnel, vibrant, sincère.
            </p>

            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="about.inspiration">
              Je puise mon inspiration chez des artistes comme <strong class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 to-soul-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-bold">Lara Fabian</strong>, que j'admire profondément. À travers chaque chanson, je cherche à transmettre une émotion vraie.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Enhanced Stats Section -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-12 pt-8">
            <div class="text-center group">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105">
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-soul-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-2">2024</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium" data-i18n="about.yearOfConsecration">Année de consécration</div>
                <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-soul-500 mx-auto mt-3 rounded-full"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center group">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105">
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-600 to-soul-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-2">2</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium" data-i18n="about.awardsWon">Prix remportés</div>
                <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500 to-soul-500 mx-auto mt-3 rounded-full"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Musical Influences -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-music rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <span class="text-white text-sm">♪</span>
              </span>
              Influences musicales
            </h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Blues</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-soul-100 text-soul-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Soul</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-accent-100 text-accent-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Variétés</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Francophone</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>